<p>&quot;Void is a tool of bourgeois oppression.&quot; Tanksy was steering with his knees while typing up podcast scripts on his phone. They were cruising at a solid 15 above the speed limit; Felicity wanted to get through Wisconsin as fast as possible, so they could hit Minneapolis tonight and start the long drive down to Texas in the morning. &quot;Also they permabanned me for doxxing Trotskyists.&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;How many flags did you have in your handle? Was it like, 'Tanksy 🇨🇳 🇸🇾 🇨🇺 🇰🇵 🇻🇳 🇻🇪 🇸🇯'?&quot;</p>
